{"tid":359191,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"有無sle患者，一齊入黎傾傾","createTime":"2017-08-14T10:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T14:22:34.000Z","uid":68839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd697242b6e4f80fc3a44b45af1c17ab604c1c6f","tid":359191,"uid":68839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:01:55.000Z","msg":"第一次用朋友account開post，請各位多多指教。<br />\n小弟確診sle七年，初時關節痛，之後有晚抖唔到氣入完醫院，發現心包膜積水，之後先知原來係sle。初頭幾年都係食類固醇，之後病情開始穩定，過住正常人生活，但個病其實會一路潛伏，最近個病開始黎料攻擊腎臟，好怕自己好唔返，成世都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b366bc82bb5e5b980ba11cc3f119741d7809ad69","tid":359191,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16dc6bfdc6bf870bdb35e9983f31113549b2f40","tid":359191,"uid":88282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會周不是抖唔到氣?"},{"pid":"7f75dd17a2ab2b4476caa4b174fb37d50de737eb","tid":359191,"uid":135294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:43:11.000Z","msg":"我都食緊類固醇 共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19732c38616eb06b6bbbf5a799954b1b5d8e7fab","tid":359191,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:55:02.000Z","msg":"類固醇, 咩藥名? 有咩副作用? 有冇肥到?"},{"pid":"a13c6a9b15559c19ceffd67915dbf079c7dd406c","tid":359191,"uid":68839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:58:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會周不是抖唔到氣?</blockquote><br />\n唔會，不過呢個病其實會攻擊所有器官，包括個腦，所以抖唔到氣相對係小事，最怕佢攻擊個腦攪到變低能仔"},{"pid":"38731ebf41fecceb2d02957625092a8db36bda96","tid":359191,"uid":68839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都食緊類固醇 共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油！類固醇其實好多副作用，不過無得揀谷住食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5676b88a9aa12aecc03d7ed96f0fb3ddf98f7381","tid":359191,"uid":68839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:03:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>類固醇, 咩藥名? 有咩副作用? 有冇肥到?</blockquote><br />\n可以參考下<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.skh.org.tw/Neuro/mg/takecare/reaction.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.skh.org.tw%2FNeuro%2Fmg%2Ftakecare%2Freaction.htm&d=cqbi2kXyh4JtWBI989%2FLTIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=72004321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.skh.org.tw/Neuro/mg/takecare/reaction.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n劑量多會食到口腫面腫，外觀上都會睇到有分別"},{"pid":"10625c5ba1174396d39d78c006240d7ab6f325d9","tid":359191,"uid":68839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"推post希望有同病相連的巴絲入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d5442415b6062fd53648809ab86d14eecdf99c","tid":359191,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"有冇變月亮臉？"},{"pid":"9a93f814ba618ab6c6e2faa9cbc2e495d43a02d4","tid":359191,"uid":68839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇變月亮臉？</blockquote>姐係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生粒粒？"},{"pid":"15bf601d8cd4ded44dd6f2e76daae5bc98ccc203","tid":359191,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>類固醇, 咩藥名? 有咩副作用? 有冇肥到?</blockquote><br />\n可以參考下<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.skh.org.tw/Neuro/mg/takecare/reaction.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.skh.org.tw%2FNeuro%2Fmg%2Ftakecare%2Freaction.htm&d=cqbi2kXyh4JtWBI989%2FLTIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=72004321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.skh.org.tw/Neuro/mg/takecare/reaction.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n劑量多會食到口腫面腫，外觀上都會睇到有分別</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03bc470776e2bb9219fb11df6e51c14df40f5363","tid":359191,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T13:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇變月亮臉？</blockquote>姐係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生粒粒？</blockquote><br />\n唔止雙下巴，直情有三四個下巴 🌝"},{"pid":"f4d338aa1792c89802c3e4bb464382b8f2e2591b","tid":359191,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"樓主係絲打？ 隻病會唔會遺傳？"},{"pid":"11579d28457c478323c588126b886bd30325ae90","tid":359191,"uid":68839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係絲打？ 隻病會唔會遺傳？</blockquote><br />\n我係巴，男有sle的機率好低，而我就係被選中的一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醫生話無證據會或唔會遺傳，因為我家人都無呢隻病，但係我有。不過，如果想有下一代就有遺傳的風險"},{"pid":"7748e147e8242c65be8fa9267f571d37d890ff0d","tid":359191,"uid":68839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇變月亮臉？</blockquote>姐係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生粒粒？</blockquote><br />\n唔止雙下巴，直情有三四個下巴 🌝</blockquote><br />\n🌝暫時無，但識人食到有三下巴"}]}